[{"Code":"en","Title":"EasyStore","Slug":"easystore","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7x-o7wqpr-002\" data-start=\"122\" data-end=\"410\">EasyStore is a powerful e-commerce platform designed to help businesses easily build and manage their online stores. It offers customizable themes, marketing tools, order management, and supports various payment methods — making it a great choice for sellers across Southeast Asia.</p><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7y-ecdrbp-003\" data-start=\"412\" data-end=\"487\">Follow this guide to start integrating <strong>Xendit</strong> with your EasyStore shop.</p><h3 data-block-id=\"md1rzx7y-jhs7v8-004\" data-start=\"494\" data-end=\"517\"><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7y-3s7f37-005\" data-start=\"519\" data-end=\"575\">Before integrating Xendit with EasyStore, make sure you:</p><ul data-block-id=\"md1rzx7y-ywq8oe-006\" data-start=\"577\" data-end=\"816\"><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7y-le3nkp-007\" data-start=\"577\" data-end=\"640\"><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7y-6qbbuz-008\" data-start=\"579\" data-end=\"640\">Have an active <strong>EasyStore</strong> account (any plan is supported).</p></li><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7y-y6og67-009\" data-start=\"641\" data-end=\"727\"><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7y-zkyjn3-010\" data-start=\"643\" data-end=\"727\">Are registered with <strong>Xendit</strong>, and have access to your <strong>API key</strong> and <strong>Business ID</strong>.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-4us4pu-011\" data-start=\"728\" data-end=\"816\"><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-xwwjv7-012\" data-start=\"730\" data-end=\"816\">Have removed any IP whitelist settings from your Xendit Dashboard (if previously set).</p></li></ul><h3 data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-yy0bp9-013\" data-start=\"823\" data-end=\"846\"><strong>Installation</strong></h3><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-icpnhp-014\" data-start=\"848\" data-end=\"931\">Follow these steps to start accepting payments on your EasyStore shop using Xendit:</p><p data-block-id=\"me5q0ct4-i7k4y9-030\" data-start=\"848\" data-end=\"931\"><video src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Screen%20Recording%202025-08-07%20at%2015.40.45.mov\" mediatype=\"video\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" data-type=\"media-content\" style=\"display:flex;margin-right:auto;width:640px;height:360px;\" controls=\"true\">null</video></p><ol data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-5wb379-015\" start=\"1\" data-start=\"933\" data-end=\"1517\"><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-34j1fn-016\" data-start=\"933\" data-end=\"1008\"><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-6chkeh-017\" data-start=\"936\" data-end=\"1008\">Log in to your <strong>Xendit Dashboard</strong>, and go to the <strong>Integrations</strong> tab.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-dtfrl7-018\" data-start=\"1009\" data-end=\"1083\"><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-coioq1-019\" data-start=\"1012\" data-end=\"1083\">Search for <strong>EasyStore</strong> under available plugins and click <strong>Install</strong>.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-ln4xm2-020\" data-start=\"1084\" data-end=\"1168\"><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-jk67d5-021\" data-start=\"1087\" data-end=\"1168\">You’ll be redirected to EasyStore’s app marketplace to setup your Xendit account in <strong>EasyStore Admin Panel &gt; Settings &gt; Payments</strong>.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-l0o6c6-026\" data-start=\"1343\" data-end=\"1449\"><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-qkdk08-027\" data-start=\"1346\" data-end=\"1449\">Select <strong>Xendit</strong> and configure your preferred payment channels (e.g., bank transfer, eWallets, cards).</p></li><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-24074f-022\" data-start=\"1169\" data-end=\"1259\"><p data-block-id=\"me5qdwh2-e982st-039\" data-start=\"1172\" data-end=\"1259\">Insert your <code>Xendit’s Business ID</code> as <code>Merchant ID</code>, and <code>Xendit’s Public API Key</code> as  <code>Secret Key</code> in Easystore’s Xendit setup page </p></li><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-z9rfeu-028\" data-start=\"1450\" data-end=\"1517\"><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-tzssw0-029\" data-start=\"1453\" data-end=\"1517\">Click <strong>Save</strong> — you’re now ready to accept payments via Xendit.</p></li></ol><section class=\"internal-notes\" data-permitted-all-team-members=\"true\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i00s-i7loi9-033\"><strong>Private notes</strong></p><h2 data-block-id=\"mem6i4dd-6nwbwk-036\" data-start=\"520\" data-end=\"539\">How EasyStore works for regional merchant</h2><h3 data-block-id=\"mem6i4dd-qtk7r1-037\" data-start=\"541\" data-end=\"578\"><strong>Activation for Local Channels</strong></h3><ul data-block-id=\"mem6i4dd-7ux32w-038\" data-start=\"579\" data-end=\"786\"><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4dd-sagpyv-039\" data-start=\"579\" data-end=\"663\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-2vhj1w-040\" data-start=\"581\" data-end=\"663\">Merchants must be activated for the specific channel (e.g., <strong>DANA</strong>) in Xendit.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-zzi73r-041\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontStyle:italic\" data-start=\"664\" data-end=\"786\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-r6xm62-042\" data-start=\"666\" data-end=\"786\"><em>Only a limited set of local channels is available for regional accounts, since these are treated as foreign merchants.</em></p></li></ul><h3 data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-tm0qtf-043\" data-start=\"788\" data-end=\"828\"><strong>EasyStore Multi-Currency Setting</strong></h3><ul data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-alvyoo-044\" data-start=\"829\" data-end=\"1065\"><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-lpfzv1-045\" data-start=\"829\" data-end=\"895\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-9h59dk-046\" data-start=\"831\" data-end=\"895\">EasyStore supports <strong>multiple checkout currencies per store</strong>.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-her6h0-047\" data-start=\"896\" data-end=\"973\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-5l192y-048\" data-start=\"898\" data-end=\"973\">This means a single store can accept <strong>IDR, PHP, MYR, etc.</strong> at checkout.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-ruxcbq-049\" data-start=\"974\" data-end=\"1065\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-cf9gbk-050\" data-start=\"976\" data-end=\"1065\">Merchants do <strong>not</strong> need to create separate stores for each currency (unlike Shopify).</p></li></ul><h3 data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-b4j6fm-051\" data-start=\"1067\" data-end=\"1099\"><strong>UI vs. Checkout Currency</strong></h3><ul data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-87tmnc-052\" data-start=\"1100\" data-end=\"1394\"><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-m4z2jh-053\" data-start=\"1100\" data-end=\"1193\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-3sphdk-054\" data-start=\"1102\" data-end=\"1193\">EasyStore’s storefront can display prices in multiple currencies for customer experience.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-s28ncj-055\" data-start=\"1194\" data-end=\"1294\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-42d33d-056\" data-start=\"1196\" data-end=\"1294\">At checkout, customers can <strong>choose their preferred currency</strong> (if the merchant has enabled it).</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-hft9tm-057\" data-start=\"1295\" data-end=\"1394\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-ceifx9-058\" data-start=\"1297\" data-end=\"1394\">This makes it easier for customers to pay in the right local currency for each payment channel.</p></li></ul><hr class=\"hr-divider1\"><h2 data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-0alpq8-059\" data-start=\"1401\" data-end=\"1452\">Flow Example: HK Merchant Wants to Accept DANA</h2><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-vp9m62-060\" data-start=\"1454\" data-end=\"1475\"><strong>Merchant setup:</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-qb3e2a-061\" data-start=\"1476\" data-end=\"1655\"><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-qlj515-062\" data-start=\"1476\" data-end=\"1500\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-d6khrg-063\" data-start=\"1478\" data-end=\"1500\">Location: Hong Kong.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-apghrq-064\" data-start=\"1501\" data-end=\"1540\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-fu5u3i-065\" data-start=\"1503\" data-end=\"1540\">Xendit balance options: USD or HKD.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-bdd5gr-066\" data-start=\"1541\" data-end=\"1598\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-a7wtgv-067\" data-start=\"1543\" data-end=\"1598\">EasyStore checkout currencies enabled: IDR, PHP, MYR.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-vbck8e-068\" data-start=\"1599\" data-end=\"1655\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-zjmscx-069\" data-start=\"1601\" data-end=\"1655\">DANA channel activated in Xendit (regional account).</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-fvw3m4-070\" data-start=\"1657\" data-end=\"1683\"><strong>Customer experience:</strong></p><ol data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-zog175-071\" start=\"1\" data-start=\"1684\" data-end=\"1976\"><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-qr6lco-072\" data-start=\"1684\" data-end=\"1751\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-kh3z0p-073\" data-start=\"1687\" data-end=\"1751\">Customer browses the EasyStore site in HKD (display currency).</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-mka992-074\" data-start=\"1752\" data-end=\"1819\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-ntftv2-075\" data-start=\"1755\" data-end=\"1819\">At checkout, customer selects <strong>IDR</strong> as the payment currency.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-wtd4eq-076\" data-start=\"1820\" data-end=\"1869\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-zlh0b8-077\" data-start=\"1823\" data-end=\"1869\">EasyStore generates a Xendit invoice in IDR.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-u3gpa5-078\" data-start=\"1870\" data-end=\"1901\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-1xq35c-079\" data-start=\"1873\" data-end=\"1901\">Customer selects <strong>DANA</strong>.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-smtv07-080\" data-start=\"1902\" data-end=\"1949\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-gh9nn8-081\" data-start=\"1905\" data-end=\"1949\">DANA payment page shows the amount in IDR.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-1opj7r-082\" data-start=\"1950\" data-end=\"1976\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-c3ea9h-083\" data-start=\"1953\" data-end=\"1976\">Customer pays in IDR.</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-qmunr8-084\" data-start=\"1978\" data-end=\"1995\"><strong>Settlement:</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-p3lp3a-085\" data-start=\"1996\" data-end=\"2211\"><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-3momn4-086\" data-start=\"1996\" data-end=\"2039\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-0jgmza-087\" data-start=\"1998\" data-end=\"2039\">Xendit receives funds from DANA in IDR.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-ylxkzz-088\" data-start=\"2040\" data-end=\"2139\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-p22wgb-089\" data-start=\"2042\" data-end=\"2139\">Xendit converts IDR to the merchant’s settlement currency (USD or HKD) using Xendit’s FX rates.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-skm42e-090\" data-start=\"2140\" data-end=\"2211\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-w6gi2o-091\" data-start=\"2142\" data-end=\"2211\">This FX conversion is where Xendit monetizes regional transactions.</p></li></ul></section><p data-block-id=\"mem6i00s-066zmd-035\"></p>","SeoTitle":"EasyStore","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"EasyStore","Slug":"easystore","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7x-o7wqpr-002\" data-start=\"122\" data-end=\"410\">EasyStore adalah platform e-commerce canggih yang dirancang untuk membantu bisnis membangun dan mengelola toko online mereka dengan mudah. Platform ini menawarkan tema yang dapat disesuaikan, alat pemasaran, manajemen pesanan, dan mendukung berbagai metode pembayaran — menjadikannya pilihan tepat bagi penjual di seluruh Asia Tenggara.</p><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7y-ecdrbp-003\" data-start=\"412\" data-end=\"487\">Ikuti panduan ini untuk mulai mengintegrasikan <strong>Xendit</strong> dengan toko EasyStore Anda.</p><h3 data-block-id=\"md1rzx7y-jhs7v8-004\" data-start=\"494\" data-end=\"517\"><strong>Persyaratan</strong></h3><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7y-3s7f37-005\" data-start=\"519\" data-end=\"575\">Sebelum mengintegrasikan Xendit dengan EasyStore, pastikan Anda:</p><ul data-block-id=\"md1rzx7y-ywq8oe-006\" data-start=\"577\" data-end=\"816\"><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7y-le3nkp-007\" data-start=\"577\" data-end=\"640\"><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7y-6qbbuz-008\" data-start=\"579\" data-end=\"640\">Memiliki akun <strong>EasyStore</strong> yang aktif (semua paket didukung).</p></li><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7y-y6og67-009\" data-start=\"641\" data-end=\"727\"><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7y-zkyjn3-010\" data-start=\"643\" data-end=\"727\">Terdaftar di <strong>Xendit</strong>, dan memiliki akses ke <strong>API key</strong> dan <strong>Business ID</strong> Anda.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-4us4pu-011\" data-start=\"728\" data-end=\"816\"><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-xwwjv7-012\" data-start=\"730\" data-end=\"816\">Telah menghapus pengaturan IP whitelist dari Dasbor Xendit Anda (jika sebelumnya diatur).</p></li></ul><h3 data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-yy0bp9-013\" data-start=\"823\" data-end=\"846\"><strong>Instalasi</strong></h3><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-icpnhp-014\" data-start=\"848\" data-end=\"931\">Ikuti langkah-langkah berikut untuk mulai menerima pembayaran di toko EasyStore Anda menggunakan Xendit:</p><p data-block-id=\"me5q0ct4-i7k4y9-030\" data-start=\"848\" data-end=\"931\"><video src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Screen%20Recording%202025-08-07%20at%2015.40.45.mov\" mediatype=\"video\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" data-type=\"media-content\" style=\"display:flex;margin-right:auto;width:640px;height:360px;\" controls=\"true\">null</video></p><ol data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-5wb379-015\" start=\"1\" data-start=\"933\" data-end=\"1517\"><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-34j1fn-016\" data-start=\"933\" data-end=\"1008\"><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-6chkeh-017\" data-start=\"936\" data-end=\"1008\">Masuk ke <strong>Dasbor Xendit</strong> Anda, dan buka tab <strong>Integrations</strong>.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-dtfrl7-018\" data-start=\"1009\" data-end=\"1083\"><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-coioq1-019\" data-start=\"1012\" data-end=\"1083\">Cari <strong>EasyStore</strong> di bawah plugin yang tersedia dan klik <strong>Install</strong>.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-ln4xm2-020\" data-start=\"1084\" data-end=\"1168\"><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-jk67d5-021\" data-start=\"1087\" data-end=\"1168\">Anda akan diarahkan ke app marketplace EasyStore untuk mengatur akun Xendit Anda di <strong>EasyStore Admin Panel &gt; Settings &gt; Payments</strong>.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-l0o6c6-026\" data-start=\"1343\" data-end=\"1449\"><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-qkdk08-027\" data-start=\"1346\" data-end=\"1449\">Pilih <strong>Xendit</strong> dan konfigurasikan saluran pembayaran pilihan Anda (misalnya, transfer bank, eWallet, kartu).</p></li><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-24074f-022\" data-start=\"1169\" data-end=\"1259\"><p data-block-id=\"me5qdwh2-e982st-039\" data-start=\"1172\" data-end=\"1259\">Masukkan <code>Xendit’s Business ID</code> Anda sebagai <code>Merchant ID</code>, dan <code>Xendit’s Public API Key</code> Anda sebagai <code>Secret Key</code> di halaman pengaturan Xendit Easystore </p></li><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-z9rfeu-028\" data-start=\"1450\" data-end=\"1517\"><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-tzssw0-029\" data-start=\"1453\" data-end=\"1517\">Klik <strong>Save</strong> — Anda sekarang siap menerima pembayaran melalui Xendit.</p></li></ol><section class=\"internal-notes\" data-permitted-all-team-members=\"true\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i00s-i7loi9-033\"><strong>Catatan pribadi</strong></p><h2 data-block-id=\"mem6i4dd-6nwbwk-036\" data-start=\"520\" data-end=\"539\">Cara Kerja EasyStore untuk merchant regional</h2><h3 data-block-id=\"mem6i4dd-qtk7r1-037\" data-start=\"541\" data-end=\"578\"><strong>Aktivasi untuk Saluran Lokal</strong></h3><ul data-block-id=\"mem6i4dd-7ux32w-038\" data-start=\"579\" data-end=\"786\"><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4dd-sagpyv-039\" data-start=\"579\" data-end=\"663\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-2vhj1w-040\" data-start=\"581\" data-end=\"663\">Merchant harus diaktifkan untuk saluran tertentu (misalnya, <strong>DANA</strong>) di Xendit.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-zzi73r-041\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontStyle:italic\" data-start=\"664\" data-end=\"786\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-r6xm62-042\" data-start=\"666\" data-end=\"786\"><em>Hanya serangkaian saluran lokal terbatas yang tersedia untuk akun regional, karena ini diperlakukan sebagai merchant asing.</em></p></li></ul><h3 data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-tm0qtf-043\" data-start=\"788\" data-end=\"828\"><strong>Pengaturan Multi-Mata Uang EasyStore</strong></h3><ul data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-alvyoo-044\" data-start=\"829\" data-end=\"1065\"><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-lpfzv1-045\" data-start=\"829\" data-end=\"895\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-9h59dk-046\" data-start=\"831\" data-end=\"895\">EasyStore mendukung <strong>beberapa mata uang checkout per toko</strong>.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-her6h0-047\" data-start=\"896\" data-end=\"973\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-5l192y-048\" data-start=\"898\" data-end=\"973\">Ini berarti satu toko dapat menerima <strong>IDR, PHP, MYR, dll.</strong> saat checkout.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-ruxcbq-049\" data-start=\"974\" data-end=\"1065\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-cf9gbk-050\" data-start=\"976\" data-end=\"1065\">Merchant <strong>tidak</strong> perlu membuat toko terpisah untuk setiap mata uang (tidak seperti Shopify).</p></li></ul><h3 data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-b4j6fm-051\" data-start=\"1067\" data-end=\"1099\"><strong>UI vs. Mata Uang Checkout</strong></h3><ul data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-87tmnc-052\" data-start=\"1100\" data-end=\"1394\"><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-m4z2jh-053\" data-start=\"1100\" data-end=\"1193\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-3sphdk-054\" data-start=\"1102\" data-end=\"1193\">Etalase EasyStore dapat menampilkan harga dalam berbagai mata uang untuk pengalaman pelanggan.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-s28ncj-055\" data-start=\"1194\" data-end=\"1294\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-42d33d-056\" data-start=\"1196\" data-end=\"1294\">Saat checkout, pelanggan dapat <strong>memilih mata uang pilihan mereka</strong> (jika merchant telah mengaktifkannya).</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-hft9tm-057\" data-start=\"1295\" data-end=\"1394\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-ceifx9-058\" data-start=\"1297\" data-end=\"1394\">Ini memudahkan pelanggan untuk membayar dalam mata uang lokal yang tepat untuk setiap saluran pembayaran.</p></li></ul><hr class=\"hr-divider1\"><h2 data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-0alpq8-059\" data-start=\"1401\" data-end=\"1452\">Contoh Alur: Merchant HK Ingin Menerima DANA</h2><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-vp9m62-060\" data-start=\"1454\" data-end=\"1475\"><strong>Pengaturan merchant:</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-qb3e2a-061\" data-start=\"1476\" data-end=\"1655\"><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-qlj515-062\" data-start=\"1476\" data-end=\"1500\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-d6khrg-063\" data-start=\"1478\" data-end=\"1500\">Lokasi: Hong Kong.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-apghrq-064\" data-start=\"1501\" data-end=\"1540\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-fu5u3i-065\" data-start=\"1503\" data-end=\"1540\">Opsi saldo Xendit: USD atau HKD.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-bdd5gr-066\" data-start=\"1541\" data-end=\"1598\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-a7wtgv-067\" data-start=\"1543\" data-end=\"1598\">Mata uang checkout EasyStore yang diaktifkan: IDR, PHP, MYR.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-vbck8e-068\" data-start=\"1599\" data-end=\"1655\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-zjmscx-069\" data-start=\"1601\" data-end=\"1655\">Saluran DANA diaktifkan di Xendit (akun regional).</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-fvw3m4-070\" data-start=\"1657\" data-end=\"1683\"><strong>Pengalaman pelanggan:</strong></p><ol data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-zog175-071\" start=\"1\" data-start=\"1684\" data-end=\"1976\"><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-qr6lco-072\" data-start=\"1684\" data-end=\"1751\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-kh3z0p-073\" data-start=\"1687\" data-end=\"1751\">Pelanggan menjelajahi situs EasyStore dalam HKD (mata uang tampilan).</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-mka992-074\" data-start=\"1752\" data-end=\"1819\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-ntftv2-075\" data-start=\"1755\" data-end=\"1819\">Saat checkout, pelanggan memilih <strong>IDR</strong> sebagai mata uang pembayaran.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-wtd4eq-076\" data-start=\"1820\" data-end=\"1869\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-zlh0b8-077\" data-start=\"1823\" data-end=\"1869\">EasyStore membuat invoice Xendit dalam IDR.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-u3gpa5-078\" data-start=\"1870\" data-end=\"1901\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-1xq35c-079\" data-start=\"1873\" data-end=\"1901\">Pelanggan memilih <strong>DANA</strong>.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-smtv07-080\" data-start=\"1902\" data-end=\"1949\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-gh9nn8-081\" data-start=\"1905\" data-end=\"1949\">Halaman pembayaran DANA menunjukkan jumlah dalam IDR.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-1opj7r-082\" data-start=\"1950\" data-end=\"1976\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-c3ea9h-083\" data-start=\"1953\" data-end=\"1976\">Pelanggan membayar dalam IDR.</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-qmunr8-084\" data-start=\"1978\" data-end=\"1995\"><strong>Penyelesaian (Settlement):</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-p3lp3a-085\" data-start=\"1996\" data-end=\"2211\"><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-3momn4-086\" data-start=\"1996\" data-end=\"2039\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-0jgmza-087\" data-start=\"1998\" data-end=\"2039\">Xendit menerima dana dari DANA dalam IDR.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-ylxkzz-088\" data-start=\"2040\" data-end=\"2139\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-p22wgb-089\" data-start=\"2042\" data-end=\"2139\">Xendit mengonversi IDR ke mata uang penyelesaian (settlement) merchant (USD atau HKD) menggunakan kurs FX Xendit.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-skm42e-090\" data-start=\"2140\" data-end=\"2211\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-w6gi2o-091\" data-start=\"2142\" data-end=\"2211\">Konversi FX ini adalah cara Xendit memonetisasi transaksi regional.</p></li></ul></section><p data-block-id=\"mem6i00s-066zmd-035\"></p>","SeoTitle":"EasyStore","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"EasyStore","Slug":"easystore","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7x-o7wqpr-002\" data-start=\"122\" data-end=\"410\">EasyStore เป็นแพลตฟอร์มอีคอมเมิร์ซที่ทรงพลัง ซึ่งออกแบบมาเพื่อช่วยให้ธุรกิจสร้างและจัดการร้านค้าออนไลน์ได้อย่างง่ายดาย แพลตฟอร์มนี้มีธีมที่ปรับแต่งได้, เครื่องมือทางการตลาด, การจัดการคำสั่งซื้อ, และรองรับวิธีการชำระเงินที่หลากหลาย — ทำให้เป็นตัวเลือกที่ยอดเยี่ยมสำหรับผู้ขายทั่วเอเชียตะวันออกเฉียงใต้</p><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7y-ecdrbp-003\" data-start=\"412\" data-end=\"487\">ทำตามคำแนะนำนี้เพื่อเริ่มต้นการเชื่อมต่อ <strong>Xendit</strong> เข้ากับร้านค้า EasyStore ของคุณ</p><h3 data-block-id=\"md1rzx7y-jhs7v8-004\" data-start=\"494\" data-end=\"517\"><strong>ข้อกำหนดเบื้องต้น</strong></h3><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7y-3s7f37-005\" data-start=\"519\" data-end=\"575\">ก่อนที่จะเชื่อมต่อ Xendit กับ EasyStore โปรดตรวจสอบให้แน่ใจว่าคุณ:</p><ul data-block-id=\"md1rzx7y-ywq8oe-006\" data-start=\"577\" data-end=\"816\"><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7y-le3nkp-007\" data-start=\"577\" data-end=\"640\"><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7y-6qbbuz-008\" data-start=\"579\" data-end=\"640\">มีบัญชี <strong>EasyStore</strong> ที่ใช้งานอยู่ (รองรับทุกแพ็กเกจ)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7y-y6og67-009\" data-start=\"641\" data-end=\"727\"><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7y-zkyjn3-010\" data-start=\"643\" data-end=\"727\">ได้ลงทะเบียนกับ <strong>Xendit</strong> และสามารถเข้าถึง <strong>API key</strong> และ <strong>Business ID</strong> ของคุณได้</p></li><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-4us4pu-011\" data-start=\"728\" data-end=\"816\"><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-xwwjv7-012\" data-start=\"730\" data-end=\"816\">ได้ลบการตั้งค่า IP whitelist ออกจาก Xendit Dashboard แล้ว (หากเคยตั้งค่าไว้ก่อนหน้านี้)</p></li></ul><h3 data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-yy0bp9-013\" data-start=\"823\" data-end=\"846\"><strong>การติดตั้ง</strong></h3><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-icpnhp-014\" data-start=\"848\" data-end=\"931\">ทำตามขั้นตอนเหล่านี้เพื่อเริ่มรับชำระเงินบนร้านค้า EasyStore ของคุณโดยใช้ Xendit:</p><p data-block-id=\"me5q0ct4-i7k4y9-030\" data-start=\"848\" data-end=\"931\"><video src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Screen%20Recording%202025-08-07%20at%2015.40.45.mov\" mediatype=\"video\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" data-type=\"media-content\" style=\"display:flex;margin-right:auto;width:640px;height:360px;\" controls=\"true\">null</video></p><ol data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-5wb379-015\" start=\"1\" data-start=\"933\" data-end=\"1517\"><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-34j1fn-016\" data-start=\"933\" data-end=\"1008\"><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-6chkeh-017\" data-start=\"936\" data-end=\"1008\">เข้าสู่ระบบ <strong>Xendit Dashboard</strong> ของคุณ และไปที่แท็บ <strong>Integrations</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-dtfrl7-018\" data-start=\"1009\" data-end=\"1083\"><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-coioq1-019\" data-start=\"1012\" data-end=\"1083\">ค้นหา <strong>EasyStore</strong> ใต้ปลั๊กอินที่มีอยู่ และคลิก <strong>Install</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-ln4xm2-020\" data-start=\"1084\" data-end=\"1168\"><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-jk67d5-021\" data-start=\"1087\" data-end=\"1168\">คุณจะถูกนำไปยัง EasyStore’s app marketplace เพื่อตั้งค่าบัญชี Xendit ของคุณใน <strong>EasyStore Admin Panel &gt; Settings &gt; Payments</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-l0o6c6-026\" data-start=\"1343\" data-end=\"1449\"><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-qkdk08-027\" data-start=\"1346\" data-end=\"1449\">เลือก <strong>Xendit</strong> และกำหนดค่าช่องทางการชำระเงินที่คุณต้องการ (เช่น bank transfer, eWallets, cards)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-24074f-022\" data-start=\"1169\" data-end=\"1259\"><p data-block-id=\"me5qdwh2-e982st-039\" data-start=\"1172\" data-end=\"1259\">ใส่ <code>Xendit’s Business ID</code> เป็น <code>Merchant ID</code> และ <code>Xendit’s Public API Key</code> เป็น <code>Secret Key</code> ในหน้าตั้งค่า Xendit ของ Easystore </p></li><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-z9rfeu-028\" data-start=\"1450\" data-end=\"1517\"><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-tzssw0-029\" data-start=\"1453\" data-end=\"1517\">คลิก <strong>Save</strong> — ตอนนี้คุณพร้อมที่จะรับชำระเงินผ่าน Xendit แล้ว</p></li></ol><section class=\"internal-notes\" data-permitted-all-team-members=\"true\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i00s-i7loi9-033\"><strong>Private notes</strong></p><h2 data-block-id=\"mem6i4dd-6nwbwk-036\" data-start=\"520\" data-end=\"539\">How EasyStore works for regional merchant</h2><h3 data-block-id=\"mem6i4dd-qtk7r1-037\" data-start=\"541\" data-end=\"578\"><strong>Activation for Local Channels</strong></h3><ul data-block-id=\"mem6i4dd-7ux32w-038\" data-start=\"579\" data-end=\"786\"><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4dd-sagpyv-039\" data-start=\"579\" data-end=\"663\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-2vhj1w-040\" data-start=\"581\" data-end=\"663\">Merchants must be activated for the specific channel (e.g., <strong>DANA</strong>) in Xendit.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-zzi73r-041\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontStyle:italic\" data-start=\"664\" data-end=\"786\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-r6xm62-042\" data-start=\"666\" data-end=\"786\"><em>Only a limited set of local channels is available for regional accounts, since these are treated as foreign merchants.</em></p></li></ul><h3 data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-tm0qtf-043\" data-start=\"788\" data-end=\"828\"><strong>EasyStore Multi-Currency Setting</strong></h3><ul data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-alvyoo-044\" data-start=\"829\" data-end=\"1065\"><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-lpfzv1-045\" data-start=\"829\" data-end=\"895\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-9h59dk-046\" data-start=\"831\" data-end=\"895\">EasyStore supports <strong>multiple checkout currencies per store</strong>.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-her6h0-047\" data-start=\"896\" data-end=\"973\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-5l192y-048\" data-start=\"898\" data-end=\"973\">This means a single store can accept <strong>IDR, PHP, MYR, etc.</strong> at checkout.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-ruxcbq-049\" data-start=\"974\" data-end=\"1065\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-cf9gbk-050\" data-start=\"976\" data-end=\"1065\">Merchants do <strong>not</strong> need to create separate stores for each currency (unlike Shopify).</p></li></ul><h3 data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-b4j6fm-051\" data-start=\"1067\" data-end=\"1099\"><strong>UI vs. Checkout Currency</strong></h3><ul data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-87tmnc-052\" data-start=\"1100\" data-end=\"1394\"><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-m4z2jh-053\" data-start=\"1100\" data-end=\"1193\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-3sphdk-054\" data-start=\"1102\" data-end=\"1193\">EasyStore’s storefront can display prices in multiple currencies for customer experience.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-s28ncj-055\" data-start=\"1194\" data-end=\"1294\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-42d33d-056\" data-start=\"1196\" data-end=\"1294\">At checkout, customers can <strong>choose their preferred currency</strong> (if the merchant has enabled it).</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-hft9tm-057\" data-start=\"1295\" data-end=\"1394\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-ceifx9-058\" data-start=\"1297\" data-end=\"1394\">This makes it easier for customers to pay in the right local currency for each payment channel.</p></li></ul><hr class=\"hr-divider1\"><h2 data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-0alpq8-059\" data-start=\"1401\" data-end=\"1452\">Flow Example: HK Merchant Wants to Accept DANA</h2><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-vp9m62-060\" data-start=\"1454\" data-end=\"1475\"><strong>Merchant setup:</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-qb3e2a-061\" data-start=\"1476\" data-end=\"1655\"><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-qlj515-062\" data-start=\"1476\" data-end=\"1500\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-d6khrg-063\" data-start=\"1478\" data-end=\"1500\">Location: Hong Kong.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-apghrq-064\" data-start=\"1501\" data-end=\"1540\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-fu5u3i-065\" data-start=\"1503\" data-end=\"1540\">Xendit balance options: USD or HKD.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-bdd5gr-066\" data-start=\"1541\" data-end=\"1598\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-a7wtgv-067\" data-start=\"1543\" data-end=\"1598\">EasyStore checkout currencies enabled: IDR, PHP, MYR.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-vbck8e-068\" data-start=\"1599\" data-end=\"1655\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-zjmscx-069\" data-start=\"1601\" data-end=\"1655\">DANA channel activated in Xendit (regional account).</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-fvw3m4-070\" data-start=\"1657\" data-end=\"1683\"><strong>Customer experience:</strong></p><ol data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-zog175-071\" start=\"1\" data-start=\"1684\" data-end=\"1976\"><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-qr6lco-072\" data-start=\"1684\" data-end=\"1751\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-kh3z0p-073\" data-start=\"1687\" data-end=\"1751\">Customer browses the EasyStore site in HKD (display currency).</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-mka992-074\" data-start=\"1752\" data-end=\"1819\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-ntftv2-075\" data-start=\"1755\" data-end=\"1819\">At checkout, customer selects <strong>IDR</strong> as the payment currency.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-wtd4eq-076\" data-start=\"1820\" data-end=\"1869\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-zlh0b8-077\" data-start=\"1823\" data-end=\"1869\">EasyStore generates a Xendit invoice in IDR.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-u3gpa5-078\" data-start=\"1870\" data-end=\"1901\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-1xq35c-079\" data-start=\"1873\" data-end=\"1901\">Customer selects <strong>DANA</strong>.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-smtv07-080\" data-start=\"1902\" data-end=\"1949\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-gh9nn8-081\" data-start=\"1905\" data-end=\"1949\">DANA payment page shows the amount in IDR.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-1opj7r-082\" data-start=\"1950\" data-end=\"1976\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-c3ea9h-083\" data-start=\"1953\" data-end=\"1976\">Customer pays in IDR.</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-qmunr8-084\" data-start=\"1978\" data-end=\"1995\"><strong>Settlement:</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-p3lp3a-085\" data-start=\"1996\" data-end=\"2211\"><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-3momn4-086\" data-start=\"1996\" data-end=\"2039\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-0jgmza-087\" data-start=\"1998\" data-end=\"2039\">Xendit receives funds from DANA in IDR.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-ylxkzz-088\" data-start=\"2040\" data-end=\"2139\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-p22wgb-089\" data-start=\"2042\" data-end=\"2139\">Xendit converts IDR to the merchant’s settlement currency (USD or HKD) using Xendit’s FX rates.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-skm42e-090\" data-start=\"2140\" data-end=\"2211\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-w6gi2o-091\" data-start=\"2142\" data-end=\"2211\">This FX conversion is where Xendit monetizes regional transactions.</p></li></ul></section><p data-block-id=\"mem6i00s-066zmd-035\"></p>","SeoTitle":"EasyStore","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"EasyStore","Slug":"easystore","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7x-o7wqpr-002\" data-start=\"122\" data-end=\"410\">EasyStore es una potente plataforma de e-commerce diseñada para ayudar a los comercios a construir y administrar fácilmente sus tiendas en línea. Ofrece temas personalizables, herramientas de marketing, gestión de pedidos y es compatible con varios métodos de pago, lo que la convierte en una excelente opción para los vendedores de todo el Sudeste Asiático.</p><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7y-ecdrbp-003\" data-start=\"412\" data-end=\"487\">Siga esta guía para comenzar a integrar <strong>Xendit</strong> con su tienda EasyStore.</p><h3 data-block-id=\"md1rzx7y-jhs7v8-004\" data-start=\"494\" data-end=\"517\"><strong>Requisitos</strong></h3><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7y-3s7f37-005\" data-start=\"519\" data-end=\"575\">Antes de integrar Xendit con EasyStore, asegúrese de que usted:</p><ul data-block-id=\"md1rzx7y-ywq8oe-006\" data-start=\"577\" data-end=\"816\"><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7y-le3nkp-007\" data-start=\"577\" data-end=\"640\"><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7y-6qbbuz-008\" data-start=\"579\" data-end=\"640\">Tenga una <strong>Cuenta</strong> activa de <strong>EasyStore</strong> (se admite cualquier plan).</p></li><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7y-y6og67-009\" data-start=\"641\" data-end=\"727\"><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7y-zkyjn3-010\" data-start=\"643\" data-end=\"727\">Esté registrado en <strong>Xendit</strong> y tenga acceso a su <strong>API key</strong> y su <strong>Business ID</strong>.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-4us4pu-011\" data-start=\"728\" data-end=\"816\"><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-xwwjv7-012\" data-start=\"730\" data-end=\"816\">Haya eliminado cualquier configuración de lista blanca de IP (IP whitelist settings) de su Xendit Dashboard (si se configuró previamente).</p></li></ul><h3 data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-yy0bp9-013\" data-start=\"823\" data-end=\"846\"><strong>Instalación</strong></h3><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-icpnhp-014\" data-start=\"848\" data-end=\"931\">Siga estos pasos para comenzar a aceptar pagos en su tienda EasyStore usando Xendit:</p><p data-block-id=\"me5q0ct4-i7k4y9-030\" data-start=\"848\" data-end=\"931\"><video src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Screen%20Recording%202025-08-07%20at%2015.40.45.mov\" mediatype=\"video\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" data-type=\"media-content\" style=\"display:flex;margin-right:auto;width:640px;height:360px;\" controls=\"true\">null</video></p><ol data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-5wb379-015\" start=\"1\" data-start=\"933\" data-end=\"1517\"><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-34j1fn-016\" data-start=\"933\" data-end=\"1008\"><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-6chkeh-017\" data-start=\"936\" data-end=\"1008\">Inicie sesión en su <strong>Xendit Dashboard</strong> y vaya a la pestaña <strong>Integrations</strong>.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-dtfrl7-018\" data-start=\"1009\" data-end=\"1083\"><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-coioq1-019\" data-start=\"1012\" data-end=\"1083\">Busque <strong>EasyStore</strong> en los plugins disponibles y haga clic en <strong>Install</strong>.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-ln4xm2-020\" data-start=\"1084\" data-end=\"1168\"><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-jk67d5-021\" data-start=\"1087\" data-end=\"1168\">Será redirigido al marketplace de aplicaciones de EasyStore para configurar su cuenta Xendit en <strong>EasyStore Admin Panel &gt; Settings &gt; Payments</strong>.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-l0o6c6-026\" data-start=\"1343\" data-end=\"1449\"><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-qkdk08-027\" data-start=\"1346\" data-end=\"1449\">Seleccione <strong>Xendit</strong> y configure sus canales de pago preferidos (por ejemplo, transferencia bancaria, E-Wallets, tarjetas).</p></li><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-24074f-022\" data-start=\"1169\" data-end=\"1259\"><p data-block-id=\"me5qdwh2-e982st-039\" data-start=\"1172\" data-end=\"1259\">Inserte su <code>Xendit’s Business ID</code> como <code>Merchant ID</code>, y su <code>Xendit’s Public API Key</code> como <code>Secret Key</code> en la página de configuración de Xendit de Easystore </p></li><li data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-z9rfeu-028\" data-start=\"1450\" data-end=\"1517\"><p data-block-id=\"md1rzx7z-tzssw0-029\" data-start=\"1453\" data-end=\"1517\">Haga clic en <strong>Save</strong> — ahora está listo para aceptar pagos a través de Xendit.</p></li></ol><section class=\"internal-notes\" data-permitted-all-team-members=\"true\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i00s-i7loi9-033\"><strong>Notas privadas</strong></p><h2 data-block-id=\"mem6i4dd-6nwbwk-036\" data-start=\"520\" data-end=\"539\">Cómo funciona EasyStore para el comercio regional</h2><h3 data-block-id=\"mem6i4dd-qtk7r1-037\" data-start=\"541\" data-end=\"578\"><strong>Activación para Canales Locales</strong></h3><ul data-block-id=\"mem6i4dd-7ux32w-038\" data-start=\"579\" data-end=\"786\"><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4dd-sagpyv-039\" data-start=\"579\" data-end=\"663\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-2vhj1w-040\" data-start=\"581\" data-end=\"663\">Los comercios deben estar activados para el canal específico (por ejemplo, <strong>DANA</strong>) en Xendit.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-zzi73r-041\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontStyle:italic\" data-start=\"664\" data-end=\"786\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-r6xm62-042\" data-start=\"666\" data-end=\"786\"><em>Solo un conjunto limitado de canales locales está disponible para cuentas regionales, ya que estas se tratan como comercios extranjeros.</em></p></li></ul><h3 data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-tm0qtf-043\" data-start=\"788\" data-end=\"828\"><strong>Configuración Multimoneda de EasyStore</strong></h3><ul data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-alvyoo-044\" data-start=\"829\" data-end=\"1065\"><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-lpfzv1-045\" data-start=\"829\" data-end=\"895\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-9h59dk-046\" data-start=\"831\" data-end=\"895\">EasyStore admite <strong>múltiples monedas de pago por tienda</strong>.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-her6h0-047\" data-start=\"896\" data-end=\"973\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-5l192y-048\" data-start=\"898\" data-end=\"973\">Esto significa que una sola tienda puede aceptar <strong>IDR, PHP, MYR, etc.</strong> al momento del pago.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-ruxcbq-049\" data-start=\"974\" data-end=\"1065\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-cf9gbk-050\" data-start=\"976\" data-end=\"1065\">Los comercios **no** necesitan crear tiendas separadas para cada Moneda (a diferencia de Shopify).</p></li></ul><h3 data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-b4j6fm-051\" data-start=\"1067\" data-end=\"1099\"><strong>Moneda de la UI vs. Moneda de Pago</strong></h3><ul data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-87tmnc-052\" data-start=\"1100\" data-end=\"1394\"><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-m4z2jh-053\" data-start=\"1100\" data-end=\"1193\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-3sphdk-054\" data-start=\"1102\" data-end=\"1193\">La interfaz de la tienda EasyStore puede mostrar precios en múltiples monedas para la experiencia del cliente.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-s28ncj-055\" data-start=\"1194\" data-end=\"1294\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-42d33d-056\" data-start=\"1196\" data-end=\"1294\">Al momento del pago, los clientes pueden <strong>elegir su moneda preferida</strong> (si el comercio lo ha habilitado).</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-hft9tm-057\" data-start=\"1295\" data-end=\"1394\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-ceifx9-058\" data-start=\"1297\" data-end=\"1394\">Esto facilita que los clientes paguen en la moneda local correcta para cada canal de pago.</p></li></ul><hr class=\"hr-divider1\"><h2 data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-0alpq8-059\" data-start=\"1401\" data-end=\"1452\">Ejemplo de Flujo: Comercio de HK Desea Aceptar DANA</h2><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-vp9m62-060\" data-start=\"1454\" data-end=\"1475\"><strong>Configuración del Comercio:</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-qb3e2a-061\" data-start=\"1476\" data-end=\"1655\"><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-qlj515-062\" data-start=\"1476\" data-end=\"1500\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-d6khrg-063\" data-start=\"1478\" data-end=\"1500\">Ubicación: Hong Kong.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4de-apghrq-064\" data-start=\"1501\" data-end=\"1540\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-fu5u3i-065\" data-start=\"1503\" data-end=\"1540\">Opciones de saldo de Xendit: USD o HKD.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-bdd5gr-066\" data-start=\"1541\" data-end=\"1598\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-a7wtgv-067\" data-start=\"1543\" data-end=\"1598\">Monedas de pago de EasyStore habilitadas: IDR, PHP, MYR.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-vbck8e-068\" data-start=\"1599\" data-end=\"1655\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-zjmscx-069\" data-start=\"1601\" data-end=\"1655\">Canal DANA activado en Xendit (cuenta regional).</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-fvw3m4-070\" data-start=\"1657\" data-end=\"1683\"><strong>Experiencia del Cliente:</strong></p><ol data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-zog175-071\" start=\"1\" data-start=\"1684\" data-end=\"1976\"><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-qr6lco-072\" data-start=\"1684\" data-end=\"1751\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-kh3z0p-073\" data-start=\"1687\" data-end=\"1751\">El cliente navega por el sitio EasyStore en HKD (moneda de visualización).</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-mka992-074\" data-start=\"1752\" data-end=\"1819\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-ntftv2-075\" data-start=\"1755\" data-end=\"1819\">Al momento del pago, el cliente selecciona <strong>IDR</strong> como la moneda de pago.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-wtd4eq-076\" data-start=\"1820\" data-end=\"1869\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-zlh0b8-077\" data-start=\"1823\" data-end=\"1869\">EasyStore genera una Factura de Xendit en IDR.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-u3gpa5-078\" data-start=\"1870\" data-end=\"1901\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-1xq35c-079\" data-start=\"1873\" data-end=\"1901\">El cliente selecciona <strong>DANA</strong>.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-smtv07-080\" data-start=\"1902\" data-end=\"1949\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-gh9nn8-081\" data-start=\"1905\" data-end=\"1949\">La página de pago de DANA muestra el Monto en IDR.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-1opj7r-082\" data-start=\"1950\" data-end=\"1976\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-c3ea9h-083\" data-start=\"1953\" data-end=\"1976\">El cliente paga en IDR.</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-qmunr8-084\" data-start=\"1978\" data-end=\"1995\"><strong>Liquidación:</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-p3lp3a-085\" data-start=\"1996\" data-end=\"2211\"><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-3momn4-086\" data-start=\"1996\" data-end=\"2039\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-0jgmza-087\" data-start=\"1998\" data-end=\"2039\">Xendit recibe fondos de DANA en IDR.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-ylxkzz-088\" data-start=\"2040\" data-end=\"2139\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-p22wgb-089\" data-start=\"2042\" data-end=\"2139\">Xendit convierte IDR a la moneda de Liquidación del comercio (USD o HKD) utilizando las tasas FX de Xendit.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-skm42e-090\" data-start=\"2140\" data-end=\"2211\"><p data-block-id=\"mem6i4df-w6gi2o-091\" data-start=\"2142\" data-end=\"2211\">Esta conversión FX es donde Xendit monetiza las Transacciones regionales.</p></li></ul></section><p data-block-id=\"mem6i00s-066zmd-035\"></p>","SeoTitle":"EasyStore","Description":null}]